                     <interp inst="t18420613-1987-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18420613-cd-242" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420613-1987-offence-1 t18420613-cd-242"></join>19th of May</rs>, 1 purse, value 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 3 shillings, 1 sixpence, 4 pence, and 5 half-pence; the property of <persName id="t18420613-name-1366" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-1366" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-1366" type="surname" value="HALL"></interp>
